    <item>
      <title>Threshold</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/poetry/threshold/</link>
      <pubDate>Wed, 22 Jan 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/poetry/threshold/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Between the lamp and the window&lt;br&gt;&#xA;there is a country I return to —&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;not sleep, not waking,&lt;br&gt;&#xA;but that particular amber&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;where the day&lt;br&gt;&#xA;unstitches itself from me&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;and I become&lt;br&gt;&#xA;briefly, briefly&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;nobody&amp;rsquo;s.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
